"segunda medida sirve para realizar el ajuste de rampa. Las medidas se "
"deben introducir en una tabla como la siguiente:"
msgstr ""
"The first measurement can correct what is called a zero adjustment. The "
"second measurement is used to perform the ramp adjustment. The "
"measurements must be entered in a table such as the following:"


